dbo:Agriculture rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Climate
dbo:Climate rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Climatology
dbo:Climatology rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Company
dbo:Company rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/DrainageBasin
dbo:DrainageBasin rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/LandCover
dbo:LandCover rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/MeteoStation
dbo:MeteoStation rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Population
dbo:Population rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/RoadSegment
dbo:RoadSegment rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Tourism
dbo:Tourism rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/WaterDerivation
dbo:WaterDerivation rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Watercourse
dbo:Watercourse rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://example.org/ontology/HealthDistrict
:HealthDistrict rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://example.org/ontology/HealthRegion
:HealthRegion rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://example.org/ontology/IFFICause
:IFFICause rdf:type owl:Class ;
           rdfs:subClassOf skos:Concept ;
           rdfs:comment "TODO: Da tabella iffi_cause, trovare classe adeguata. Inventario dei Fenomeni Franosi in Italia (IFFI) - Dictionary table listing landslide causes. Each row is a cause, with a textual ID, a numeric code, a IT description text and a group (4 total + 'nd'). Each landslide in table iffi_landslide can be associated to zero or more of the causes of this table, by means of 1:N association table iffi_landslide_cause. Data of this table come from the IFFI landslide inventory shapefile from Eurac and from [C]. References: [C] https://idrogeo.isprambiente.it/api/dizionari/cause." .


###  http://example.org/ontology/IFFILandslide
:IFFILandslide rdf:type owl:Class ;
               rdfs:subClassOf ccore:Hazard ;
               rdfs:comment "Landslide recorded in the Italian Landslide Inventory (IFFI), represented as a point corresponding to the highest initiation point (PIFF)."@en ;
               rdfs:label "IFFI landslide"@en .


###  http://example.org/ontology/IffiLandslide
:IffiLandslide rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://example.org/ontology/LandCoverChange
:LandCoverChange rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://example.org/ontology/RoadNetwork
:RoadNetwork rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.semanticweb.org/crima/crima-core#Hazard
ccore:Hazard rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#ObjectProperty
rdf:ObjectProperty rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept
skos:Concept rdf:type owl:Class .


###  http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Entity
prov:Entity rdf:type owl:Class .


